@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.55 + v2 + 0.60) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.29)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(v1) - wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    v1 = 0.03
    v0 = (v1 + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.59) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.85)))
    data[tid] = v0
